OL,4,CBP: Lorry driver shortages closing some
OL,5,Csites temporarily
OL,6, Lorry driver shortages are causing
OL,7, temporary fuel supply issues at some of
OL,8, BP's petrol stations.
OL,10,FThe oil firm said shortages of unleaded
OL,11,Fpetrol and diesel had seen a "handful"
OL,12,Fof its UK sites close temporarily.
OL,14,FHowever, the oil company said the "vast
OL,15,Fmajority" of shortages were being
OL,16,F"resolved within a day".
OL,18,FBP said its supply chain had also been
OL,19,Fexacerbated by the closure of a
OL,20,Fdistribution terminal due to staff
OL,21,Fbeing told to isolate last week.
